Author: violettheatre
Text: Yay! I love trying new food and eating at nice restaurants so I just fast all day too and try and enjoy my meal as much as possible even though I sometimes wake up in the middle of the night feeling anxious thinking about what I ate afterward. Going out can be fun if you can manage the scariness, glad you had a good time in the end. :)
